tweet: To everyone still up wrapping presents (& to those super-organized folks who are already done): May the blessings of the season be upon you & may you be surrounded by hope, peace, joy & love. Merry Christmas to all & to all a good night! #MerryChristmas

Thank you to all our troops who are serving far from home. And thank you to all the military families out there who make sacrifices for their loved ones & our nation. We are grateful for everything you do. #MerryChristmas

Senate Republicans don’t seem to have the votes (nor unanimous support in their caucus) for House bill that includes $5Billion for the wall Trump said Mexico would pay for. We are working in good faith to avoid a wasteful #shutdown & urge Pres Trump to call off shutdown threat.

Librarians usually like things quiet, but I hope they give themselves a big, loud cheer tonight bc they helped pass my Museum & Library Services Act (S. 3530) to help #libraries & #museums upgrade technology, better serve their communities, & boost our educational infrastructure.

Today, the full US Senate voted 50-49 to overturn Trump Admin’s #darkmoney rule that exempts some organizations from disclosing large donors to the IRS. This is a positive step for fair elections. Now the House must also act on bipartisan basis.

US Senate voted 87-13 to pass bipartisan #FarmBill. Several key wins for RI #farmers & families: will help small farms, feed families in need, boost local farmers markets, enhance conservation, legalize industrial #hemp, & expand #cropinsurance access to #shellfish growers.

Great to be w/ @USDOT @SecElaineChao & my former law school classmate, Deputy #DOT Sec. Jeff Rosen, & my former high school classmate, @RIDOTNews Dir. Peter Alviti, to announce new #BUILD investments to upgrade America’s transportation network. pic.twitter.com/fw9stLhBCl

Tomorrow the Senate will vote on @SenatorTester’s bill to protect our democracy & overturn the Trump Admin’s controversial #darkmoney rule shielding donors from the IRS. I will vote to help shed light on dark money & hold special interests accountable by increasing transparency.
